{"type": "article", "id": 20557, "title": "像飞机机翼的衣柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-12T07:13:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122323PLDnqb3XINc941mi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是由荷兰设计师 Mieke Meijer 设计的衣柜，他从 20 世纪早期飞机机翼中获得的灵感。柜子的表面像是有无数小方格，其实是用带孔的橡木板搭建的，中间串上钢丝绳固定，从中间打开后就有木质机翼的轻盈感。里面的隔间也是用带孔的橡木板，很透气。它的重量只有 18.5 千克，方便移动。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122321C9BkO2sJTvuDeU8d.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122321fUCplHjFwyD6ZQ37.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122322asGhDkgZIrB2Vp4x.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122322H9iKceowsU042guZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122323IXr8Hz3yS6ej2oTa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}